# HVDC System Data Analysis and Optimization

This project simulates, analyzes, and optimizes data for a High Voltage Direct Current (HVDC) power system. Using synthetic HVDC data, the application performs basic data analysis, anomaly detection, and optimization to maximize system efficiency. The project also visualizes trends and relationships within the data, saving each visualization as a PNG file for easy reference.

